            <== Macam Macam Event dalam DOOM ==>
1. Mouse Event = ketika mouse dikclick , double click , dan ada juga digeser 
                pointernya
2. Keyboard Event = ketika keyboard ditekan , dilepas dll 
3. Resources Event = ketika halaman diload , 
4. Focus Event = penting saat buat Font ketika teks atua inputan di click 
                masuknya ke focus
5. View Event 
6. Form Event 
7. CSS Animation & Transition Event 
8. Drag & Drop Event 
9. dll           

        .after(namaElement); => Setelahnya
        => cara bangkitkan warna random dengan method 
        
         button.addEventListener('click' , function(){
        const r = Math.round(Math.random() * 255 + 1);
        const g = Math.round(Math.random() * 255 + 1);
        const b = Math.round(Math.random() * 255 + 1);
        console.log(r);
        document.body.style.backgroundColor = 'rgb('+ r +','+ g +','+ b +')';
    });

            => Kategori di Mouse Event 
            .   click
            .   dblclick
            .   mouseover
            .   mouseenter
            .   mouseup
            .   wheel
            .   ....

            => Kategori Keyboard Event 
            .   keydown
            .   keypress 
            .   keyup

            => View Event 
            .   resize
            .   scroll

            => Form Event 
            .   reset 
            .   submit

=> Event untuk slider input type='range'; ada Event 'change'            



